Package: multivrs
Title: Automated Multiverse Analysis Powered by LLM Analyst Agents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Aleksandar", "Tomašević", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "atomashevic@gmail.com")
Description: Provides tools for automated multiverse analysis through a
    five-stage pipeline: data input, research question formulation,
    decision space discovery, multiverse execution, and
    aggregation/reporting. Integrates LLM analyst agents for
    specification discovery and supports specification curve
    visualization.
